{"tid":600800,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得香港機場係世界第一","createTime":"2018-03-21T15:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T08:06:44.000Z","uid":7699,"like":47,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d27bbd655cd55eaeb6fab64b21faf91e4998584f","tid":600800,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:44:17.000Z","msg":"首先交通黎講已經好方便 基本上半個鐘內已經出到市區 同埋基本上交通配套都完善 喺市區任何一個地方都有方法直達機場（唔計的士）<br />\n<br />\n其次就係客運量同流量都係世界最top 但比起外國又極少出現混亂 雖然成日都過唔夠人手運行李 但對比起外國都已經算快 只係我地行e道太快 去埋個廁所10分鐘都唔駛就出到去等行李<br />\n<br />\n第三就係就算早左入機場都唔會悶 入到禁區又多野行多野睇 仲有好多餐廳 唯一要彈嘅就係好撚貴 但入到去貴啲都正路"},{"pid":"8e9e3b8dd5ee80b98473c861d1e97c8492af1835","tid":600800,"uid":163911,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"香港細姐"},{"pid":"e9a76405242fe9d24188c881550160a7d8772347","tid":600800,"uid":65012,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"青馬橋收皮就變孤島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7847c8236baf692bd7659cc9e5cfc98c046c0a7","tid":600800,"uid":7699,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"仲有arrival同departure 分2層都唔係個個先進機場做到"},{"pid":"20bd74067b9cac9e19fee5b9bbf6e4e64b4b9012","tid":600800,"uid":7699,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e9a76405242fe9d24188c881550160a7d8772347","tid":600800,"uid":65012,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"青馬橋收皮就變孤島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"上層炒車都仲可以行下層 除非極端到冧橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61de45ec55c6e32cb6311a684b245e3e16d61daa","tid":600800,"uid":33770,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"20bd74067b9cac9e19fee5b9bbf6e4e64b4b9012","tid":600800,"uid":7699,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e9a76405242fe9d24188c881550160a7d8772347","tid":600800,"uid":65012,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"青馬橋收皮就變孤島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"上層炒車都仲可以行下層 除非極端到冧橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:08:59.000Z","msg":"上次咪試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起碼要整多條出屯門"},{"pid":"866ac42978a4a1d19037530e70cfde7225256aeb","tid":600800,"uid":100131,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:17:07.000Z","msg":"莫斯科機場都唔錯, 上次去轉機覺得幾商場<br />\n<br />\n不過原本有2個鐘等轉機, 但去程delay咗一個鐘, 結果一落地, 過海關, 去到另一個閘口已經無時間, 我去個登機口好鬼細, 唔知其他登機口係咪咁"},{"pid":"30a9191b3ce1f63a551713ac05744f44c72bf147","tid":600800,"uid":7854,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"你都on撚9  香港豆潤咁細 番市區唔通要半日咩"},{"pid":"34285a63c12fd19d44e6e08d7b26366d10152ebb","tid":600800,"uid":139176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:24:08.000Z","msg":"機場wifi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7694f3625ae33ea770b92bb7c5824b4378f61ee","tid":600800,"uid":74302,"like":24,"dislike":7,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:25:28.000Z","msg":"你去過新加坡機場未？<br />\n一個廿年既機場仲想世界第一？你以為個世界圍住香港轉唔變呀?<br />\n得罪一句，大陸新機場 係你講行街食野果方面都好過香港機場啦。<br />\n香港機場出行李慢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過去日本 一行出來就棟左我個喼 仲要有專人去協助乘客<br />\n<br />\n香港細 咪快去到囉<br />\n唯一優點係<br />\n落機抵達好快<br />\n因為係香港人用E道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  快過其他地方自己抵達"},{"pid":"0f3aafaabd69b086f65fe4b6b557f98f592e0b5b","tid":600800,"uid":80110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:27:24.000Z","msg":"人工就係世界第一底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefcab80ff0205c9533d3526146a25b8bfbf95e6","tid":600800,"uid":1785,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:32:24.000Z","msg":"仲有人拎香港機場打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234eaf7ecc6df0a6f3c4559b3b3a8e0d23f675cc","tid":600800,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61de45ec55c6e32cb6311a684b245e3e16d61daa","tid":600800,"uid":33770,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"20bd74067b9cac9e19fee5b9bbf6e4e64b4b9012","tid":600800,"uid":7699,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e9a76405242fe9d24188c881550160a7d8772347","tid":600800,"uid":65012,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"青馬橋收皮就變孤島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"上層炒車都仲可以行下層 除非極端到冧橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:08:59.000Z","msg":"上次咪試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起碼要整多條出屯門"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T16:50:14.000Z","msg":"出屯門咪起緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b797d42046228ca81cd7dcb863b3ed5b3ea84dca","tid":600800,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"